# Privacy Policy

This Privacy Policy outlines the manner in which our mobile application (hereinafter referred to as "the App") collects, employs, and discloses your data. The App is dedicated to sustaining robust privacy protections for all its users. This Privacy Policy is formulated to assist you in understanding the way we handle and use any personal information you decide to share, and to help guide you in making informed decisions when using the App.

By accessing or using the App, you are consenting to the practices described in this Privacy Policy. If you disagree with this policy, kindly refrain from using the App. Please be aware that we reserve the right to modify this policy periodically, thus we encourage regular reviews. Your continued use of the App signifies your acceptance of our modified Privacy Policy.

## 1. Data We Collect

As of the current state, the App does not collect any personal data. The design of the App is such that it stores all data pertaining to your food within the device itself and lacks any functionality to collect your personal data.

## 2. Data Storage and Protection

The data you enter is stored on your device and is not accessible to anyone other than yourself unless the data on your device is shared by you or your device provider.

## 3. Future Updates

Should there be a future update that allows user data upload for functionalities such as synchronization, we assure you that we will not disclose this information to any third parties. If such features are added, we will accordingly update our privacy policy and make an announcement.

## 4. Changes to Our Privacy Policy

The App reserves the right to modify this policy as well as our Terms of Service at any given time. Should there be significant changes to our Privacy Policy, we will notify users by sending a notice to the primary email address specified in your account or by posting a prominent notice on our site. Such significant changes will become effective 30 days following such notification. Non-material alterations or clarifications will take effect immediately. We recommend you periodically visit the Site and this privacy page for updates.

## Contact Us

Should you have any inquiries regarding this Privacy Policy or the practices of this Site, please feel free to contact us by sending an email to forgerwise@gmail.com.

